# Nit on Mac

Install `xcode` from the [[app store|https://itunes.apple.com/ca/app/xcode/id497799835?mt=12]]

Install `macport` from [[https://distfiles.macports.org/MacPorts/]]

Hack: make `port` usable by the tools

~~~
$ sudo ln -s /opt/local /usr/
~~~

Install packages required to compile Nit and its tools

~~~
$ sudo port install boehmgc ccache graphviz libunwind-headers
~~~

Install and compile Nit

~~~
$ git clone clone http://nitlanguage.org/nit.git
$ cd nit
$ make
~~~

Install mode package required by libs and pass the tests

~~~
$ sudo port install curl libsdl2 libsdl2_image ncurses pkgconfig 
~~~
